headline: Does Moody's Recent Fintech Partnerships Justify Its Share Price in 2025?
summary: Wondering if Moody's current share price reflects real value or just market hype? You're not alone, and we're about to break it down in plain terms. After mostly holding steady this year, Moody's stock has ticked up 1.4% year-to-date and gained over 80% in the last five years. This suggests long-term growth but also raises questions about future upside. Recent headlines have focused on Moody's expanding its risk assessment coverage and forming new partnerships in the financial technology...
